<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SHIVAY Mock Services - TCS CBT Exam Portal (Style 2)</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --tcs-blue: #0f2c59;
            --tcs-light-blue: #1e4a8a;
            --tcs-orange: #ff9933;
            --green-saved: #2d8a4e;
            --red-unanswered: #c9302c;
            --purple-review: #7b1fa2;
            --gray-unvisited: #f4f4f4;
            --border-color: #d3d3d3;
            --text-dark: #333333;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Header: Shivay Brand Logo & Shlok --- */
        .top-header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--tcs-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .shivay-logo {
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tcs-orange) 0%, #ffffff 50%, #128807 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--tcs-blue);
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
        }

        .brand-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .brand-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
        }

        .brand-subtitle {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #555;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .shlok-container {
            text-align: center;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #d35400;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
            background: #fff3e0;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--tcs-orange);
            max-width: 45%;
        }

        .exam-title-badge {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            background-color: var(--tcs-blue);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* --- Screens & Overlays --- */
        .full-screen-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(15, 44, 89, 0.95);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .portal-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 450px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--tcs-orange);
        }

        .instruction-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            width: 95%;
            max-width: 850px;
            max-height: 90vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--tcs-blue);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .instruction-box h2 {
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        /* --- Common UI elements --- */
        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .input-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
        }

        .input-group input, .input-group select, .input-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .btn-action {
            background-color: var(--tcs-blue);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-action:hover {
            background-color: var(--tcs-light-blue);
        }

        /* --- Instruction Legend Cards --- */
        .inst-legend {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .inst-color-box {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        /* --- Main Exam Layout Split --- */
        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Left Area */
        .question-panel {
            width: 70%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .q-header-bar {
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .lang-selector-top select {
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .question-area {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 25px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .q-num-badge {
            background-color: var(--tcs-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .q-text-section {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .lang-text {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .lang-text.hindi {
            color: #1a5276;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .option-label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .option-label:hover {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            border-color: var(--tcs-light-blue);
        }

        .option-label input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 12px;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            accent-color: var(--tcs-blue);
        }

        /* Right Sidebar */
        .sidebar-panel {
            width: 30%;
            background-color: #f4f5f7;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border-left: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .candidate-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .photo-box {
            width: 65px;
            height: 80px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            background-color: #eaeaea;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .photo-box svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .candidate-info {
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .candidate-info strong {
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .timer-container {
            background-color: #ffebee;
            color: var(--red-unanswered);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        /* Grid Palette Scroll */
        .palette-container {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 15px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .palette-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .grid-matrix {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .grid-item {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            background-color: var(--gray-unvisited);
            color: #333;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .grid-item.active {
            outline: 2px solid var(--tcs-light-blue);
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .legend-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            font-size: 10px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .legend-color {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .status-saved { background-color: var(--green-saved) !important; color: white !important; }
        .status-unanswered { background-color: var(--red-unanswered) !important; color: white !important; }
        .status-review { background-color: var(--purple-review) !important; color: white !important; }
        .status-unvisited { background-color: var(--gray-unvisited) !important; color: #333 !important; }

        /* --- Results & Feedbacks --- */
        .result-panel {
            flex: 1;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .analysis-dashboard {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .dashboard-header {
            background-color: var(--tcs-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .stat-card {
            padding: 15px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-card:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .stat-val {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--tcs-blue);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .stat-lbl {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .accuracy-box {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9fbfd;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .progress-bar-container {
            background-color: #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 12px;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 10px auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--green-saved);
            width: 0%;
            transition: width 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .detailed-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .detailed-table th, .detailed-table td {
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .detailed-table th {
            background-color: #f4f5f7;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* Solution Container CSS */
        .solutions-container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 25px auto;
            text-align: left;
            background: #fbfcfd;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .sol-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .sol-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .sol-text-correct {
            color: var(--green-saved);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .sol-text-user {
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        /* --- Footer Action Buttons --- */
        .footer-bar {
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer-btn {
            padding: 10px 22px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-left-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-clear {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn-clear:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .btn-review {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: var(--purple-review);
            border-color: var(--purple-review);
        }

        .btn-review:hover {
            background-color: #e8eaf6;
        }

        .btn-save-next {
            background-color: var(--tcs-light-blue);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--tcs-light-blue);
        }

        .btn-save-next:hover {
            background-color: #1e4a8a;
        }

        /* Motivation Quote Box */
        .motivation-quote-box {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            background-color: #fcf8e3;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--tcs-orange);
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 700px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Exit Subscription CSS */
        .subscription-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .sub-btn-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .sub-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .sub-link:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .link-telegram { background-color: #0088cc; }
        .link-instagram { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 107%, #fdf497 0%, #fdf497 5%, #fd5949 45%, #d6249f 60%, #285AEB 90%); }
        .link-youtube { background-color: #ff0000; }

        .admin-footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .admin-footer a {
            color: #ff9933;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body oncontextmenu="return false;">

    <!-- REGISTRATION PORTAL -->
    <div id="registration-portal" class="full-screen-container">
        <div class="portal-box">
            <div class="shivay-logo" style="margin: 0 auto 15px auto;">S</div>
            <h2>SHIVAY MOCK SERVICES</h2>
            <p>HP Government Online Recruitment Exam Portal</p>
            
            <form id="portalForm" action="https://formsubmit.co/hemrajchauan509@gmail.com" method="POST" onsubmit="return handleRegister(event)">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="student-name">Candidate Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" id="student-name" name="Candidate Name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="student-contact">Email Address / Phone Number *</label>
                    <input type="text" id="student-contact" name="Candidate Contact" placeholder="Email Address or Phone Number" required>
                </div>

                <!-- Hidden inputs to post results via formsubmit -->
                <input type="hidden" id="hidden-score" name="Final Score">
                <input type="hidden" id="hidden-feedback" name="Performance Feedback">
                <input type="hidden" id="hidden-review-target" name="Exam Suggestion Chosen">
                <input type="hidden" id="hidden-custom-review" name="User Custom Review Text">
                <input type="hidden" id="hidden-attempt" name="Attempt Number">
                <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">

                <button type="submit" class="btn-action" style="width: 100%;">Sign In & Verify Profile</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- INSTRUCTIONS PORTAL -->
    <div id="instruction-portal" class="full-screen-container hidden">
        <div class="instruction-box">
            <h2>General Instructions / सामान्य निर्देश</h2>
            
            <div style="max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; padding-right: 10px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color:#555; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <h4 style="color:#000; margin-top:0;">English Instructions:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>The clock will be set at the server. The countdown timer in the top right corner of screen will display the remaining time available for you to complete the examination.</li>
                    <li>The Question Palette displayed on the right side of screen will show the status of each question using the specified symbols.</li>
                </ol>
                
                <div class="inst-legend">
                    <div class="inst-color-box status-unvisited">1</div>
                    <span>You have not visited the question yet. (आपने अभी तक प्रश्न नहीं देखा है।)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inst-legend">
                    <div class="inst-color-box status-unanswered">2</div>
                    <span>You have not answered the question. (आपने प्रश्न का उत्तर नहीं दिया है।)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inst-legend">
                    <div class="inst-color-box status-saved">3</div>
                    <span>You have answered the question. (आप प्रश्न का उत्तर दे चुके हैं।)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="inst-legend">
                    <div class="inst-color-box status-review">4</div>
                    <span>You have NOT answered the question, but have marked the question for review. (आपने उत्तर नहीं दिया है, बल्कि समीक्षा के लिए चिह्नित किया है।)</span>
                </div>

                <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">

                <h4 style="color:#000;">हिंदी निर्देश:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>सर्वर पर घड़ी सेट की गई है। स्क्रीन के ऊपरी दाएं कोने में काउंटडाउन टाइमर परीक्षा पूरी करने के लिए आपके पास उपलब्ध शेष समय को प्रदर्शित करेगा।</li>
                    <li>स्क्रीन के दाईं ओर प्रदर्शित प्रश्न पैलेट ऊपर दिए गए प्रतीकों का उपयोग करके प्रत्येक प्रश्न की स्थिति को दर्शाएगा।</li>
                    <li>आप बिना उत्तर दिए भी अगले प्रश्न पर जा सकते हैं, कोई भी प्रश्न अनिवार्य (compulsory) नहीं है।</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;">
                <div class="input-group" style="margin-bottom: 0; min-width: 280px;">
                    <label for="default-language" style="font-weight: bold;">Choose your default language / अपनी डिफ़ॉल्ट भाषा चुनें:</label>
                    <select id="default-language" style="padding: 8px;">
                        <option value="bilingual">Bilingual (English + Hindi)</option>
                        <option value="english">English Only</option>
                        <option value="hindi">Hindi Only</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <button class="btn-action" onclick="startActualExam()">I am ready to begin / मैं परीक्षा शुरू करने के लिए तैयार हूँ</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TCS EXAM SYSTEM FEEDBACK PORTAL -->
    <div id="review-feedback-portal" class="full-screen-container hidden">
        <div class="portal-box" style="max-width: 550px; text-align: left;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--tcs-blue); margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--tcs-orange); padding-bottom: 8px;">TCS CBT Exam Feedback & Review</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; color:#555;">Please provide your feedback before final submission. (कृपया सबमिशन से पहले अपना फीडबैक दें:)</p>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Q1. किस परीक्षा से संबंधित टेस्ट सीरीज़ और बनानी चाहिए? (Suggest Next Exam Test Series)*</label>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px;">
